Insider Activity


Individual




Lawrence P. Reinhold



Mr. Lawrence P. Reinhold is Chief Financial Officer at CompUSA.com, Inc., a Member at Financial Executives International and a Member at The American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. He is on the Board of Directors at Systemax, Inc. Mr. Reinhold was previously employed as an Independent Director by Pulse Electronics Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Greatbatch, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Critical Path, Inc., and Managing Partner by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP. He received his undergraduate degree from San Diego State University and an MBA from San Diego State University.



