Lawrence P. (Larry) Reinhold 

		
		President and CEO, 

	
		 Systemax Inc. 	

 
Last Updated: 11/21/2016 



Executive Summary
Reinhold is President and Chief Executive Officer at Systemax, a role he assumed in 2016. Previously, he served as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of the company. Prior to joining Systemax, Reinhold served as Executive Vice President and Chief Financial Officer of several companies, including Critical Path Inc. a N 
Personal Attributes and Interests

Reinhold currently resides in Port Washington, New York.

Current Focus

Company overview: Systemax, Inc., is a Fortune 1000 company based in Port Washington, New York that sells personal computers, computer supplies, consumer electronics and industrial products through multiple e-Commerce w 
Biographical Highlights

Born circa 1960.
Reinhold received both his BS in Accounting (1980-1982) and an MBA (1985-1987) from San Diego State University- California State University. 
Other Boards and Organizations

Former Member, Board of Directors, Pulse Electronics Corporation (2011 - 2013)
Member, American Institute of CPAs 
 





